{"id":1178395353,"question_id":3309,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1708223852,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1178395353/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Count Prefix and Suffix Pairs I","memory":"44.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int countPrefixSuffixPairs(String[] words) {\n        \n        int len = words.length;\n        int cnt=  0;\n        \n        for(int i=0; i<len ; i++){\n            for(int j=i+1; j<len; j++){\n                \n                String a = words[i];\n                String b = words[j];\n                \n                if(isps(a,b)){\n                    cnt++;\n                }\n                \n            }\n        }\n        \n        return cnt;\n        \n    }\n    \n    private boolean isps(String a, String b ){\n        \n        if(b.length()<a.length()) return  false;\n        \n        String p = b.substring(0, a.length());\n        String s = b.substring(b.length()-a.length(), b.length());\n        \n        return a.equals(p) && a.equals(s);\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"count-prefix-and-suffix-pairs-i","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
